cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

The paper deals with fast binary descriptors for vision-based applications, which are commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The proposed method involves adapting the descriptor to different image regions, which could fall under machine learning (cs.LG) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of fisheye cameras, which could also relate to multimedia (cs.MM) applications.
